<P>INKLE and YARICO: AN OPERA, IN THREE ACTS. AS PERFORMED AT THE <HI>THEATRE-ROYAL</HI> IN THE HAY-MARKET, On SATURDAY, AUGUST 11th, 1787.</P>
<P>WRITTEN BY GEORGE COLMAN, Junior.</P>
<P><HI>LONDON</HI>: Printed for G. G. J. and J. ROBINSON, PATER-NOSTER-ROW.</P>
</DIV1>
